  "short_description": "John's got a hunch something's up on Lush Palms island. There's this eerie gas affecting the military base, chem lab and locals... Time to jump in and investigate who’s behind it! Unveil the story! Discover the map! Obtain resources! Survive among the infected! Solve the puzzles! Fight your way!🌴",
